
                               termjutsu.sh
                        <terminal ninja techniques>


§ installation
git clone https://github.com/getjared/termjutsu.git
cd termjutsu
chmod +x termjutsu.sh
./termjutsu.sh

§ dependencies
• bash shell
• unicode/emoji support in your terminal
• basic unix utilities
• terminal with color support
• • • sudo pacman -S noto-fonts noto-fonts-cjk noto-fonts-emoji

§ quick-start
commands:
list                    : show all available jutsu
exit                    : quit the program
[jutsu name]            : perform the specified jutsu

configuration:
termjutsu is designed to be simple and extensible. new jutsu can be added by modifying the arrays in the source code:
    JUTSU_PATTERNS - for emoji patterns
    JUTSU_JAPANESE - for japanese names

running termjutsu:
    ./termjutsu.sh
or add to your path:
    sudo cp termjutsu.sh /usr/local/bin/termjutsu
    termjutsu

example jutsus:
• rasengan (らせんがん) - spiral sphere technique
• chidori (千鳥) - lightning blade
• fireball (火遁・豪火球の術) - great fireball technique
• and many more!

all patterns support unicode emoji and multi-line animations for complex jutsu visualizations.
feel free to add more or do whatever you like to it..
